title: Bebble's Langos
typeOfFood: Lacto, Fast food, Take-out, Hungarian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Hungarian with a British twist, its menu is based around the food Langos, a traditional Hungarian street food that is cooked to order. The dough is vegan, and there are a variety of sweet and savory topping and fillings. Husband and wife operated, can answer questions about ingredients, offer different vegan puddings with prior notice.
